      <title>交易商评估 Beryl 的影响并为美联储做准备，油价保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-9</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着最严重的风暴贝丽尔 (Beryl) 过去，油价在连续两天下跌后趋于稳定，美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔 (Jerome Powell) 将发布货币政策报告，该报告将影响人们对大宗商品等风险资产的更广泛情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-9</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 23:21:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
